'''Jiovany Javier Ramos Díaz''' (born 26 January 1997) is a Panamanian [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[centre-back]] for [[Venezuelan Primera División]] side [[Academia Puerto Cabello|Puerto Cabello]], on loan from [[C.A. Independiente de La Chorrera|CAI]], and the [[Panama national football team|Panama national team]].

==International career==
Ramos made his debut for the [[Panama national football team|Panama national team]] in a 0–0 friendly tie with [[Nicaragua national football team|Nicaragua]] on 26 February 2020.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://int.soccerway.com/matches/2020/02/26/world/non-fifa-friendlies/nicaragua/panama/3211005/|title=Nicaragua vs. Panama – 26 February 2020|website=Soccerway}}</ref>

